title: Anthem - Christian Scott
description:
On Anthem, the follow up to his Grammy-nominated
 Concord debut, Christian takes modern trumpet playing
 to a new level. His signature breathy, brooding sound
 combines with the haunting and emotionally powerful
 material to create an album destined to be another
 milestone in the annals of jazz.
Advance release features additional track ("Void") not
 available on retail version of CD.
